{
  "stem": "23278.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were there about a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to school in the Rhineland near Bonn, Konigswinter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before-- I mean, it was the same summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father left me, and then he came back, picked me up, and we went to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I mean, usually it wasn't done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The French didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And beside, I was quite young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he knew a business associate that took me in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Konigswinter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was just maybe, I don't know, six weeks, something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In retrospect-- he never told me what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as he-- I never asked questions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were in a hotel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a hotel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You also mentioned that this was the period of the Olympics and the Franco, the war in Spain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did you know about all of this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew that I didn't like my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I liked my life with my parents, but I had a big anguish, mostly when Hitler spoke.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father could listen and understand me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't understand everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I could see how the people stopped, most of the people in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you could-- I sensed the fear and the hysterics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now when I look back, and I see him looking so ridiculous, like a clown, I felt, how could people be mesmerized by somebody so stupid?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at the time, you didn't feel that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had fear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you and your father talk about it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father-- my parents never spoke of their business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never asked questions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Politics my--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "World politics, very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just my father said he was a dangerous man, and we might have a war again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
